        "text": "<h2><a href=\"/pages/hairmnl-studio\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"HairMNL Studio\">HairMNL Studio's Portfolio</a></h2><p>HairMNL Studio is a beauty salon that offers premium services.</p>",
