      "blocks": {
        "text_block_99TeY7": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "Color, Cut & Treatment",
            "text": "<p>At HairMNL Studio, we specialize in expert hair color, cut, smoothing and perming services to enhance your natural beauty. From personalized treatments to precision cuts, our skilled stylists will craft a look that suits your style and personality.</p>",
            "button_label": "See More",
            "button_link": "#colorandcut",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": ""
          }
        },
        "template--14665088925795__2739197d-1006-445a-a2dc-512a3d856212-text_block-1": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "Hair & Makeup",
            "text": "<p>Elevate your natural beauty with our professional hair and make-up services. Whether it’s for a wedding, a corporate event, or any special occasion, we’ll make you look and feel like your best self. Our team can craft flawless looks for you, from glowing makeup to stylish updos, and many more.</p>",
            "button_label": "See More",
            "button_link": "#hairandmakeup",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": ""
          }
        },
        "template--14665088925795__2739197d-1006-445a-a2dc-512a3d856212-text_block-2": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "Styling",
            "text": "<p>Look flawless at any occasion by having your hair styled professionally. Our expert stylists specialize in creating stunning hairstyles to complement and enhance your natural features. At HairMNL Studio, we’ll curate the perfect style to match your event.</p>",
            "button_label": "See More",
            "button_link": "#styling",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": ""
          }
        }
      },
