          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/High_Quality_Salon_Products_-_Kapitolyo.png",
            "title": "Premium Products",
            "text": "<p>We believe in quality at every step, which is why we only use premium, authentic products. We offer plant-based, vegan, and ammonia-free services that deliver exceptional results while being gentle on your hair.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc"
          }
        },
        "f62876d4-7dee-4787-862d-55729314636e": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Aftercare_-_Kapitolyo.png",
            "title": "Wide Assortment of Aftercare",
            "text": "<p>We have curated a range of premium salon aftercare and styling products. Drop by HairMNL Studio to try them yourself before purchasing!</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc"
          }
        },
        "eb84555c-9d25-4c95-b2d8-5ab33dde9a53": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/0639ea16-2e34-43eb-8ebd-ebf1135f9040.jpg",
            "title": "Bar Area",
            "text": "<p>We offer a stylish and vibrant space where we cater to your beauty needs while providing a perfect setting for special events, ensuring an unforgettable experience for you and your guests.</p>",
